    "form_header_text": "FY 2027 Programmatic & Language Appropriations Request Form",
    "form_instructions_text": "Thank you in advance for submitting your Programmatic and Language Request(s) to the Office of Congressman Chuck Edwards (NC-11). In anticipation of final guidance and deadlines from the House Appropriations Committee being released in the coming weeks for the FY27 appropriations process, please find Rep. Edwards' FY27 programmatic and language request form below. Please submit your completed FY27 Programmatic and Language request form(s) below. Our office's application deadline for programmatic and language requests will be March 6th at 5pm. For any questions, follow up, and to request a meeting about your request, please reach out to the appropriate staffer as noted below. All requests must be fully compliant with committee requirements. Below is a summary of who will handle each subcommittee: Monika Konrad - Homeland Security, THUD, Defense, NSRP, MilCon/VA; Sydney Branton - FSGG, Interior, Agriculture, Energy & Water; Dawson Connell -- LHHS, Legislative Branch, CJS. *A separate form will be utilized for CPF requests.* Call our office at (202) 225-6401 for more information.",
